                                            <small><?php _e('You can upload up to 5 files. Maximum file size: 50MB. Allowed types: PNG, JPG, JPEG, PDF, TXT, MP4, MOV, AVI, WEBM', 'support-ticket-system'); ?></small>
                                            <div class="support-ticket-file-list"></div>
